item.title: Aspose.Words for JasperReports 20.7 Release Notes
item.description: This page contains release notes of Aspose.Words for JasperReports 20.7. Important Note: Starting from release 1.9.0 there are several versions of JAR library (necessary for better support of older versions of JasperServer and JasperReports): For JasperServer For JasperReports Use the following JAR library 7.1.0 … 7.5.0 6.5.0 … 6.11.0 aspose.words.jasperreports-20.4-7.1.0-7.5.0.jar 6.4.2 … 6.4.3 6.4.2 … 6.4.21 aspose.words.jasperreports-20.7.0-6.4.2-6.4.3.jar 6.
